poll

public Command poll()
Retrieves and removes the first command in the queue that has received a reply, or null if there are no commands waiting in the queue.

Returns:
The command on which a reply arrived, or null if no replies have been received.

java.lang.InterruptedException - if another thread has interrupted the current thread.
